# FFTSetup

**Type Alias**

An opaque type that contains setup information for a given FFT transform.

## Declaration

```swift
typedef struct OpaqueFFTSetup *FFTSetup;
```

## Discussion

A setup object can be allocated with [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/kernel/1580009-vdsp_create_fftsetup] and destroyed with [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/kernel/1579978-vdsp_destroy_fftsetup]. The setup object includes, among other things, precomputed tables used in computing an FFT of the specified size.
